page.title: 15Traffic Survey on A35
page.content:
This survey was taken between 1.45 and 2.45 in the afternoon of Wednesday 26th June 1985.We noted the amont of traffic travelling east to west and west to east.The traffic that we studied was limited to the following groups: Cars;Lorries;Vans;Coaches; and motorcyles. The results of this survey are as follows: {East to West : West to East Cars.......820 {:}Cars.......883 Vans........88 {:}Vans........90 Coaches......3 {:}Coaches......7 Lorries.....22 {:}Lorries.....24 Motorcycles.13 {:}Motorcycles.18
